item.title: About
item.description: I’m an IT student and artist based in Germany 🇩🇪. When I’m not programming, I like to draw and make music. FAQ ✋ Why .moe? ✨ .moe is a fairly new top-level domain extension that I happened to come across. Why did I decide to go with this? Because it sounded pretty decent. A lot of interesting websites use this domain extension: safe.moe guya.moe themes.moe What does oaj/oatandjam mean?
